   STC Resource Clearinghouse

            What is the School-to-Career Resource Clearinghouse?

   The California School-to-Career (STC) Resource Clearinghouse is
   Californias primary location for School-to-Career information.
   Educators/business and labor organizations/students/parents/community
   representatives looking for innovative materials and resources to
   improve school/programs will find more than 1800 books, videotapes,
   lesson plans, reports, newsletters, marketing materials and discussion
   groups, etc. through the free electronic STC Resource Clearinghouse.

   Please "click" below for direct links to Components of the Resource
   Clearinghouse
     * School-to-Career Resource Library
     * School-to-Career Practices
     * Online Calendar of Events
     * Discussion Groups
     * Website Links
     * Newsletters
     * Customer Support: helpdesk@statecenter.com or Phone (559) 323-4641.

